		<smtpCredsPassword><CLIENT SECRET></smtpCredsPassword>
		EXAMPLE - CLIENT CERTIFICATE: (REMARK: The account running the script should have AT LEAST Allow:Read on the private key linked to the certificate being used)
		<smtpCredsType>EIDAPPCLIENTID_CERTIFICATE</smtpCredsType>
		<smtpCredsUserName><TENANT FQDN>\<APP CLIENT ID></smtpCredsUserName>
